quote_last: 26th; which produced, three hours later, a reply: "Delighted; please bring a No. 3 Rippingille stove" - a perplexing and ominous direction, which somehow chilled me in spite of its subject matter.
quote_raw: Thanks; expect me 9.34 p.m. 26th; which produced, three hours later, a reply: "Delighted; please bring a No. 3 Rippingille stove" - a perplexing and ominous direction, which somehow chilled me in spite of its subject matter.
title: The Riddle of the Sands
author: Erskine Childers
